claim.claim-text:
14. A method of treating an S. epidermidis infection in a subject, comprising:
screening for poly-γ-DL-glutamic acid (γDLPGA) in the subject;
enhancing an immune response against poly-γ-D-L-glutamic acid (γDLPGA) by administrating to the subject an antiserum against poly-γ-D-L-glutamic acid, thereby treating an S. epidermidis infection in a subject.
